No environment variables or system properties are indicated. Prefer in-memory stubs/mocks for DavResource, DavSessionProvider, DavLocatorFactory, servlet requests/responses, and XML/client method objects; do not assume a live Jackrabbit repository or WebDAV server is available.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"The 2.0-beta4 parent POM manages servlet-api as 2.3, while the existing scaffold uses 2.4; 2.4 is compatible with the current tests, but Gradle/native verification remains authoritative.\",\n    \"The reported failure is a native test runtime failure after image build, so setup alone may not address the failing assertions or reachability metadata needs.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_038462f0c4011710016a42a8f1479c81979065a65e1949b902\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2356, "output": 857, "cacheRead": 34304, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 37517, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782753511336, "responseId": "resp_038462f0c4011710016a42a8e7fc588197a1060f45a991e7eb"}, "toolResults": []}
